<../../../index.trig> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#6a0eefe65e1f5225f42cf5e526b6073e>.
<#6a0eefe65e1f5225f42cf5e526b6073e> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Create>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://data.aeronomie.be/dataset/4831d4b9-09eb-492c-8308-4dd553386083/resource/6cc5fbda-d171-4771-b69a-34bef114b5d7>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#published> "2026-06-15T15:32:59.949Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>.
<#6a0eefe65e1f5225f42cf5e526b6073e> {
<https://data.aeronomie.be/dataset/4831d4b9-09eb-492c-8308-4dd553386083/resource/6cc5fbda-d171-4771-b69a-34bef114b5d7> a <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#Distribution>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/title> "Electrons weekly 2020-2025 LT"@en;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "Electron fluxes observed by the EPT between January 2020 and September 2025. In this file, the data was averaged on L (the McIlwain parameter) and in time (weekly). The fluxes are thus averaged in bins of L and time.\r\n\r\nThe dataset has the following structure: \r\n\r\n###Coordinates\r\n* __name__ - _type_ - _size_ - _min_ - _max_ - description.\r\n* __time_center__ - _datetime64[ns]_ - 299 - _2020-01-05T12:00:00_ - _2025-09-14T12:00:00_ - center of the time bins.\r\n* __time_edges__ - _datetime64[ns]_ - 300 - _2019-12-26_ - _2025-09-18_ - edges of the time bins.\r\n* __L_center__ - _float64_ - 360 - _L=1.0125_ - _L=9.9875_ - center of the L bins.\r\n* __L_center__ - _float64_ - 361 - _L=1_ - _L=10_ - edges of the L bins. \r\n* __energy_center__ - _float64_ - 6 - _E=0.55 MeV_ - _E=5.2 MeV_ - center of the EPT energy channels.\r\n* __energy_edges__ - _float64_ - 7 - _E=0.5 MeV_ - _E=8.0 MeV_ - edges of the EPT energy channels._(note in the dataset the last energy channel edge is 2.5 MeV but it should be 8.0 MeV)_\r\n\r\n###Data variables\r\n* __name__ - _type_ - _(coordinates)_ - _(size)_\r\n* __data__ -  _(time_center, L_center, energy_center)_ - _(299, 360, 6)._\r\naveraged electron fluxes in the L-Time bins.\r\n\r\n\r\nNote: For python users, we recommand using the 'xarray' library to read the dataset easily."@en;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/issued> "2026-03-03T08:35:00.344632"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/modified> "2026-03-05T09:30:47.955495"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#mediaType> <https://www.iana.org/assignments/media-types/application/x-netcdf>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/format> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/file-type/NETCDF>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#accessURL> <https://data.aeronomie.be/dataset/4831d4b9-09eb-492c-8308-4dd553386083>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#downloadURL> <https://data.aeronomie.be/dataset/4831d4b9-09eb-492c-8308-4dd553386083/resource/6cc5fbda-d171-4771-b69a-34bef114b5d7/download/electrons_weekly_2020_2025_lt.nc>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/license> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/licence/CC_BY_4_0>;
    <http://data.europa.eu/r5r/availability> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/planned-availability/AVAILABLE>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#byteSize> "5186509"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#nonNegativeInteger>
}
<../../../index.trig> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#c7d0490fb2bcf6c1194c2ee900476206>.
<#c7d0490fb2bcf6c1194c2ee900476206> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Create>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://data.aeronomie.be/dataset/4831d4b9-09eb-492c-8308-4dd553386083/resource/a8ecc87c-07d8-4a59-a57b-37d411108cf5>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#published> "2026-06-15T15:32:59.953Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>.
<#c7d0490fb2bcf6c1194c2ee900476206> {
<https://data.aeronomie.be/dataset/4831d4b9-09eb-492c-8308-4dd553386083/resource/a8ecc87c-07d8-4a59-a57b-37d411108cf5> a <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#Distribution>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/title> "Electrons daily 2024-2025 LT"@en;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "Electron fluxes observed by the EPT between January 2024 and December 2024. In this file, the data was averaged on L (the McIlwain parameter) and in time (daily). The fluxes are thus averaged in bins of L and time.\r\n\r\nThe dataset has the following structure: \r\n\r\n###Coordinates\r\n* __name__ - _type_ - _size_ - _min_ - _max_ - description.\r\n* __time_center__ - _datetime64[ns]_ - 365 - _2024-01-01T12:00:00_ - _2024-12-31T12:00:00_ - center of the time bins.\r\n* __time_edges__ - _datetime64[ns]_ - 300 - _2024-01-01_ - _2024-12-31_ - edges of the time bins.\r\n* __L_center__ - _float64_ - 360 - _L=1.05_ - _L=7.95_ - center of the L bins.\r\n* __L_center__ - _float64_ - 361 - _L=1_ - _L=8_ - edges of the L bins. \r\n* __var_name__ - _str_ - 15 - _Na_ - _Na_ - name of all variables in the dataset.\r\n\r\n###Data variables\r\n* __name__ - _type_ - _(coordinates)_ - _(size)_\r\n* __data_mean__ -  _(time_center, L_center, var_name)_ - _(299, 360, 15)_ averaged variables values in the L-Time bins.\r\n* __data_std__ -  _(time_center, L_center, var_name)_ - _(299, 360, 15)_ standard deviation of the variable values in the L-Time bins.\r\n\r\n###Variable names\r\n####EPT electron energy channels\r\n*__e-fl-00__ - _channel 1_ - 0.5-0.6 MeV, \r\n*__e-fl-01__ - _channel 2_ - 0.6-0.7 MeV, \r\n*__e-fl-02__ - _channel 3_ - 0.7-0.8 MeV,\r\n*__e-fl-03__ - _channel 4_ - 0.8-1.0 MeV,\r\n*__e-fl-04__ - _channel 5_ - 1.0-2.4 MeV,\r\n*__e-fl-05__ - _channel 6_ - 2.4-8.0 MeV,\r\n\r\n####Other variables\r\n*__B__: Intensity of the magnetic field [nT],\r\n*__Long__: longitude [°],\r\n*__Lat__: latitude [°],\r\n*__PitchU__: Unilib pitch angle [°],\r\n*__BvecU-0__, __BvecU-1__, __BvecU-2__: Unilib magnetic field vectors [nT],\r\n*__LU__: Unilib McIlwain parameter [-],\r\n__MLTU__: Unilib magnetic local time [h],\r\n\r\n\r\nNote: For python users, we recommand using the 'xarray' library to read the dataset easily."@en;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/issued> "2026-03-03T09:16:47.553338"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/modified> "2026-03-05T09:54:10.553946"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#mediaType> <https://www.iana.org/assignments/media-types/application/x-netcdf>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/format> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/file-type/NETCDF>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#accessURL> <https://data.aeronomie.be/dataset/4831d4b9-09eb-492c-8308-4dd553386083>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#downloadURL> <https://data.aeronomie.be/dataset/4831d4b9-09eb-492c-8308-4dd553386083/resource/a8ecc87c-07d8-4a59-a57b-37d411108cf5/download/electrons_2024_ltimeavg_24h_t_0.1l.nc>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/license> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/licence/CC_BY_4_0>;
    <http://data.europa.eu/r5r/availability> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/planned-availability/AVAILABLE>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#byteSize> "6149270"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#nonNegativeInteger>
}
