    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/title> "Turbulence profiles"@en;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "The dataset contains turbulence measurements performed at different altitudes along the vertical gradients of the temperate mixed forest ecosystem in Vielsalm, Belgium. Deployed instruments were measuring continuously and data is reported at regular time intervals of 30 minutes. Data is provided under csv file format and information on the instrumental setup, as well as all variables reported, is detailed in the header."@en;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/issued> "2025-07-25T06:09:50.010257"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/modified> "2025-10-13T12:02:32.204216"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#mediaType> <https://www.iana.org/assignments/media-types/text/csv>;
