    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/title> "Animation 3: not"@en;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "Notch created by a short time burst enhancement in the level of geomagnetic activity determined by the value of Kp illustrated in the upper panel.  \r\nThe notch corotates with the plasmasphere."@en;
