    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "NCAR hosted ftp archive with prior atmospheric states obtained from the WACCMv6 model (Gettelman 2019, https://doi.org/10.1029/2019JD030943), extracted at the NDACC IRWG stations and averaged over a 60y time period 1980-2040. See https://wiki.ucar.edu/pages/viewpage.action?pageId=452264118 for further details."@en;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/issued> "2024-09-03T09:39:55.825202"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
