    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/title> "TLE data (auxillary)"@en;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "Set of historical two-line elements retrieved from CelesTrak through _Special Data Request_ for NORAD catalog number 52204 (Axiom-1, COSPAR ID 2022-037A).  The file received on 2025-04-11 includes 26 TLEs covering the period range from 2022-04-08 until 2022-04-25. \r\n\r\n### Credits\r\n* [CelesTrak](https://celestrak.org/) is a web-based service established by Dr. T.S. Kelso allowing the retrieval of unclassified Two-Line Element sets."@en;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/issued> "2025-06-13T12:42:42.510887"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
