    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/title> "TLE data (auxillary)"@en;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "Set of historical two-line elements retrieved from CelesTrak through _Special Data Request_ for NORAD catalog number 63427 (Fram2, COSPAR ID 2025-066A).  The file received on 2025-04-11 includes 17 TLEs covering the period range from 2025-04-01 until 2025-04-04. \r\n\r\n### Credits\r\n* [CelesTrak](https://celestrak.org/) is a web-based service established by Dr. T.S. Kelso allowing the retrieval of unclassified Two-Line Element sets."@en;
