<https://data.aeronomie.be/dataset/c5be77bb-d1de-401d-9861-5c13a4eabfbc/resource/49d96c45-4851-4759-a297-648d155f14c1> a <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#Distribution>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/title> "Instructions"@en;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "Student instructions for this exercise.  The exercise is divided in two parts:\r\n\r\n* Part a: _Calculate the total dose an astronaut would have received during the private human spaceflight mission Inspiration4_\r\n* Part b: _Calculate the total dose an astronaut would have received during one year mission for the same orbit as Inspiration4_\r\n\r\nThe document includes worksheets to be filled during the exercise.  The exercise requires internet access, a valid SPENVIS account, and the mission trajectory file."@en;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/issued> "2025-06-11T07:32:30.994631"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/modified> "2025-06-12T10:53:50.083991"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#mediaType> <https://www.iana.org/assignments/media-types/application/pdf>;
