    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "summary of the LTS ozone profiles:  \r\n\r\n| Name | Size | Bytes | Class | Attributes |  \r\n| ------- | ------- | -------- | -------- | ------------- |  \r\n| A  |  25600x20  |    4096000 |  double   |  20 first coefficients (related to the PCA in bigRun25.mat)   |   \r\n| n0  |   101x1   |      808   |  double   | arbitraty air number density [cm^-3] average profile used for all vmr conversions   |   \r\n| noz   |    25600x101 |     20684800   |  double   | all ozone number density [cm^-3] profiles   |   \r\n| ozCell   |   1x10    |    1305960  |    cell   |       same as in bigRun25.mat   |   \r\n| vmr   |   25600x101  |     20684800   |  double   | all ozone vmr [ppm] profiles |   "@en;
