    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/title> "Results files in folder “temp”"@en;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "Qgas.txt : This file contains intermediate results obtained for various values of Qgas, the comet’s gas production rate.\r\n\r\ndeltaDG.txt : This file contains intermediate results obtained for various values of deltaDG, the comet’s dust-to-gas ratio.\r\n\r\nnu.txt : This file contains intermediate results obtained for various values of nu, the comet’s gas ionization rate.\r\n\r\nvflyby.txt : This file contains intermediate results obtained for various values of vflyby, the comet flyby speed.\r\n"@en;
