    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/title> "Figures in folder “figures/pdf”"@en;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "Figures with the instrument science return values as a function of closest approach distance, for S/C A, B1, B2, respectively:  \r\n\r\n* Figure_SciReturn_Q_5.0e+28_nu_5.0e-07_deltaDG_2.0_components_A.pdf  \r\n* Figure_SciReturn_Q_5.0e+28_nu_5.0e-07_deltaDG_2.0_components_B1.pdf  \r\n* Figure_SciReturn_Q_5.0e+28_nu_5.0e-07_deltaDG_2.0_components_B2.pdf  \r\n\r\nFigure with the S/C A, B1, B2 and the mission science return values as a function of closest approach distance for S/C A:  \r\n\r\n* Figure_SciReturn_Q_5.0e+28_nu_5.0e-07_deltaDG_2.0_overview.pdf\t\r\n\r\nFigures with the science return values computed at a fixed closest approach distance xxx kilometers for S/C A:  \r\n\r\n* Figure_SciReturn_Q_5.0e+28_nu_5.0e-07_deltaDG_2.0_R_CA_A_xxx_km_dust.pdf  \r\n* Figure_SciReturn_Q_5.0e+28_nu_5.0e-07_deltaDG_2.0_R_CA_A_xxx_km_F.pdf  \r\n* Figure_SciReturn_Q_5.0e+28_nu_5.0e-07_deltaDG_2.0_R_CA_A_xxx_km_gas.pdf  \r\n* Figure_SciReturn_Q_5.0e+28_nu_5.0e-07_deltaDG_2.0_R_CA_A_xxx_km_par.pdf  \r\n* Figure_SciReturn_Q_5.0e+28_nu_5.0e-07_deltaDG_2.0_R_CA_A_xxx_km_plasma.pdf  \r\n* Figure_SciReturn_Q_5.0e+28_nu_5.0e-07_deltaDG_2.0_R_CA_A_xxx_km_rs.pdf  \r\n* Figure_SciReturn_Q_5.0e+28_nu_5.0e-07_deltaDG_2.0_R_CA_A_xxx_km_total.pdf  \r\n* Figure_SciReturn_R_CA_variation.pdf\r\n\r\nFigures showing how the closest approach distance and the mission science return change with variation of the parameters Qgas, deltaDG, nu, and vflyby :  \r\n\r\n* Figure_SciReturn_R_CA_variation.pdf   \r\n* Figure_SciReturn_H_CI_variation.pdf  "@en;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/issued> "2024-07-11T09:47:15.827081"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
