<../../../index.trig> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#bb826102b63e99507860610fc0c0fa1f>.
<#bb826102b63e99507860610fc0c0fa1f> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Create>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://data.aeronomie.be/dataset/7abdf440-8642-443d-8936-ed336e474f90/resource/5c4e3264-00a1-4cfc-8488-8dfb4e111d91>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#published> "2026-06-15T15:33:01.771Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>.
<#bb826102b63e99507860610fc0c0fa1f> {
<https://data.aeronomie.be/dataset/7abdf440-8642-443d-8936-ed336e474f90/resource/5c4e3264-00a1-4cfc-8488-8dfb4e111d91> a <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#Distribution>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/title> "Standard terms and definitions applicable to the quality assurance of Essential Climate Variable data records"@en;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "This document contains a selection of standard terms and definitions relevant \r\nto the quality assurance of Essential Climate Variable (ECVs) data records.  It \r\nreproduces  appropriate  terms  and  definitions  published  by  normalization \r\nbodies,  mainly  by  BIPM/JCGM/ISO  in  their  International  Vocabulary  of \r\nMetrology  (VIM)  [RD18]  and  Guide  to  the  Expression  of  Uncertainties  (GUM) \r\n[RD4].  It also reproduces selected terms and definitions related to the quality \r\nassurance and validation of Earth Observation (EO) data, available publicly on \r\nthe  ISO  website  and  on  the  Cal/Val  portal  of  the  Committee  on  Earth \r\nObservation  Satellites  (CEOS)  [RD2].    Several  of  those  terms  have  been \r\nrecommended  by  CEOS  in  the  GEO-CEOS  Quality  Assurance  framework  for \r\nEarth Observation (QA4EO) [RD17] and, as such, are applicable to virtually all \r\nCopernicus  data  sets  of  EO  origin.    Terms  and  definitions  are  expected  to \r\nevolve as normalization organisations regularly update their standards.  "@en;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/issued> "2024-04-25T11:24:28.327786"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/modified> "2024-06-10T12:14:00.913039"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#mediaType> <https://www.iana.org/assignments/media-types/application/pdf>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/format> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/file-type/PDF>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#accessURL> <https://data.aeronomie.be/dataset/7abdf440-8642-443d-8936-ed336e474f90>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#downloadURL> <https://data.aeronomie.be/dataset/7abdf440-8642-443d-8936-ed336e474f90/resource/5c4e3264-00a1-4cfc-8488-8dfb4e111d91/download/report_2017.pdf>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/license> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/licence/CC_BY_4_0>;
    <http://data.europa.eu/r5r/availability> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/planned-availability/AVAILABLE>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#byteSize> "863196"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#nonNegativeInteger>
}
<../../../index.trig> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#bc7efc97f1b1d899517195fc6d8c1ccc>.
<#bc7efc97f1b1d899517195fc6d8c1ccc> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Create>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://data.aeronomie.be/dataset/7abdf440-8642-443d-8936-ed336e474f90/resource/ae2459ea-4d64-4dd5-ad35-52a3785efb54>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#published> "2026-06-15T15:33:01.775Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>.
<#bc7efc97f1b1d899517195fc6d8c1ccc> {
<https://data.aeronomie.be/dataset/7abdf440-8642-443d-8936-ed336e474f90/resource/ae2459ea-4d64-4dd5-ad35-52a3785efb54> a <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#Distribution>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/title> "QUALITY ASSESSMENT OF QA4ECV CLIMATE DATA RECORDS OF  ATMOSPHERIC COMPOSITION: TERMINOLOGY, METHODOLOGY AND  APPLICATION TO TROPOSPHERIC NO 2 , HCHO AND CO FROM THE GOME-2,  IASI AND OMI SATELLITES"@en;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "Abstract: Two major objectives of the EC FP7 project Quality Assurance for Essential Climate Variables \r\n(QA4ECV) were the development of a generic quality assurance system dedicated to C3S, and the \r\ndemonstration of this generic quality assurance system on 6 pilot ECVs. In this work, we describe (i) \r\nthe terms and definitions applicable to the quality assurance that have been agreed within QA4ECV, \r\n(ii) the generic validation protocol, (iii) the QA4ECV atmosphere ECV validation server, and (iv) quality \r\nassessment results for the 3 atmospheric QA4ECV climate data records (NO 2 , HCHO and CO).\r\n\r\nOrigin: Proceedings for the 2018 EUMETSAT Meteorological Satellite Conference,  \r\n17-21 September 2018, Tallinn, Estonia. \r\n\r\nURL: https://www.eumetsat.int/media/42970"@en;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/issued> "2024-06-10T12:09:44.019223"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/modified> "2024-06-10T12:17:28.368263"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#mediaType> <https://www.iana.org/assignments/media-types/application/pdf>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/format> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/file-type/PDF>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#accessURL> <https://data.aeronomie.be/dataset/7abdf440-8642-443d-8936-ed336e474f90>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#downloadURL> <https://data.aeronomie.be/dataset/7abdf440-8642-443d-8936-ed336e474f90/resource/ae2459ea-4d64-4dd5-ad35-52a3785efb54/download/quality_assessment_qa4ecv_cdr_eumetsatproc2018_compernolle.pdf>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/license> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/licence/CC_BY_4_0>;
    <http://data.europa.eu/r5r/availability> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/planned-availability/AVAILABLE>
}
